crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: ET INFO Splashtop Domain in DNS Lookup (splashtop .com)
crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert dns $HOME_NET any -> any any (msg:"ET INFO Splashtop Domain in DNS Lookup (splashtop .com)"; dns.query; dotprefix; content:".splashtop.com"; endswith; fast_pattern; reference:url,support-splashtopbusiness.splashtop.com/hc/en-us/articles/115001811966-What-are-the-Firewall-Exceptions-and-IP-addresses-of-Splashtop-servers-Services-; classtype:misc-activity; sid:2035762; rev:2; metadata:attack_target Client_and_Server, created_at 2022_04_05, deployment Perimeter, performance_impact Low, confidence High, signature_severity Informational, tag Description_Generated_By_Proofpoint_Nexus, updated_at 2022_05_02;)

crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: APP-DETECT DNS request for Splashtop domain splashtop.com
crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert udp $HOME_NET any -> any 53 ( msg:"APP-DETECT DNS request for Splashtop domain splashtop.com"; flow:to_server; byte_test:1,!&,0xF8,2; content:"|09|splashtop|03|com|00|",fast_pattern,nocase; service:dns; reference:url,en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Splashtop; classtype:misc-activity; gid:1; sid:27930; rev:3; )
